                                    <title type="desc">Divine institutes</title>
                                    <rubric>Firmiani lactantii diuinarum institutionum aduersus gentes libri septem. Incipit primus de falsa religione. Quanti sit et fuerit semper cognitio ueritatis et quod nec sine religione sapientia nec sine sapientia nec sine sapientia fit probanda religio. I<supplied reason="omitted">hesu</supplied>m C<supplied reason="omitted">hristu</supplied>m.</rubric>
